T1  - The value of government data collection: Evidence from central bank digital currency and corporate patenting
AU  - Zhang, Guanglong
AU  - Chan, Kam C.
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 188
SP  - 107703
PY  - 2026
DA  - 2026/07/01/
